graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+]
    KubeRay -->|manages| Ray[Ray 2.0.0+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|visualization| Grafana[Grafana]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler]
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| IngressCtrl[Istio/Ingress Controller]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|expose services| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    KubeRay -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    KubeRay -->|metrics integration| MonitoringStack[ODH Monitoring Stack]

    %% External Services
    KubeRay -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry]
    Ray -->|fault tolerance| ExternalRedis[External Redis]
    Ray -->|object storage| S3[S3/GCS Storage]

    %% Integration Points
    APIServer[KubeRay APIServer] -->|manages CRs| K8s
    APIServer -.->|optional| KubeRay
    CLI[KubeRay CLI] -->|kubectl plugin| K8s
    PythonClient[Python Client] -->|programmatic| APIServer

    %% Monitoring Flow
    MonitoringStack -->|ServiceMonitor| Prometheus
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| KubeRay
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| Ray
    Grafana -->|queries| Prometheus

    %% OpenShift Specific
    Routes -->|part of| OpenShift[OpenShift Platform]
    SCC[SecurityContextConstraints] -->|part of| OpenShift
    KubeRay -->|uses| SCC

    %% Ray Dependencies
    Ray -->|runs on| K8s
    Ray -->|dashboard ingress| Routes
    Ray -->|serve ingress| Routes

